      "content": "therapists and friends.. they don't get it. they say \"it gets better\" but it just feels like everything is pointless now. like why even bother with breakfast or work or anything if the one thing that made it worth it is gone? it's just a huge, empty void. i just want the weight to stop. i want it to just be over.",
